OL,3,CMan in life critical condition after
OL,4,Ccollision with car on major A road
OL,6,FA man in his twenties has been taken
OL,7,Fto hospital with life threatening
OL,8,Finjuries after being involved in a
OL,9,Fcollision with a car on the A31 in
OL,10,FFarnham.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,13,FEastbound carriageway at the junction
OL,14,Fof Station Hill at around 9pm on
OL,15,FTuesday evening. (3 March)
OL,17,FA pedestrian, a man in his twenties
OL,18,Fwas taken to hospital with life
OL,19,Fthreatening injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
