OL,3,CMan in life critical condition after
OL,4,Ccollision with car on major A road
OL,6,FThe A31 Eastbound was closed from
OL,7,FCoxbridge roundabout and reopened at
OL,8,F3am on Wednesday morning (4 March).
OL,10,FA Surrey Police spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Our enquiries are ongoing, and no
OL,12,Farrests have been made at this time.
OL,14,F"We are asking anyone who may have
OL,15,Fwitnessed the collision to get in
OL,16,Ftouch.
OL,18,F"We are also seeking CCTV, dashcam, or
OL,19,Fhelmet cam footage that may have
OL,20,Fcaptured all or part of this incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
